Package: ggmemo
Title: Semantic Annotation Helpers for Business Charts in ggplot2
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("Lindsay", "Lintelman", , "lindsay.lintelman@posit.co",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides opinionated, high-level annotation functions for
    ggplot2 charts commonly used in business reporting. Instead of
    manually computing deltas or positioning arrows, users call semantic
    verbs like annotate_callout() and annotate_change() that handle
    formatting, placement, and styling automatically. Built on top of
    the ggpp package for precise annotation positioning.
